{"title":"La Chouette and Brother Cycles The Swoops! Singlespeed","link":"https://theradavist.com/la-chouette-and-brother-cycles-the-swoops-singlespeed/","date":1733923411000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-3.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/la-chouette-bike-shop/\" target=\"_blank\">La Chouette in Paris</a> has teamed up with the UK’s <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/brother-cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Brother Cycles</a> to design a singlespeed city bike called <a href=\"https://www.lachouetteparis.com/collections/swoops\" target=\"_blank\">The Swoops!</a> Let’s check it out…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-2.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Swoops! is the first collaborative and limited line of custom single-speed bikes designed and built on the versatile and sleek Brother Cycles All Day frame. This collection is a mix of simplicity and urban cycling style, brought to life with the expert paint job by the Stolen Garage team, using a beautiful Rolls Royce blue, with pink glitter for a touch of pazazz!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-12.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-12.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-12.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-12.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-13.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-13.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-13.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-13.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-14.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-14.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Each bike is assembled at La Chouette where the wheels are hand built and each bike rolls out of the doors of the shop.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-10.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-10.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Each frame has this eye-catching custom paint job and is kitted out with incredible components from Simworks, Bassi, and Shimano. These bikes are built for city cruising, offering a comfortable and stylish ride, with 700 x 38 Volummy tires that ensure the bike “Swoops” wherever you go, whether it’s tarmac, cobbles, or even off-road.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-11.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/LaChouette_Brother_Cycles_Singlespeed-11.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Swoops! is available as a complete bike for €2.300 or a frame and fork for €1.200. See more at <a href=\"https://www.lachouetteparis.com/collections/swoops\" target=\"_blank\">La Chouette</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/la-chouette-and-brother-cycles-the-swoops-singlespeed/\">La Chouette and Brother Cycles The Swoops! Singlespeed</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"dac6e9514e135b20f887194505e4f705040bfc0b6f9d9ad212af14a85684f7fc","category":"Cycling"}